Apart from missing children

183
00:09:49,490 --> 00:09:50,770
or private commissions,

184
00:09:50,770 --> 00:09:52,770
the Special Investigation Department
only handles

185
00:09:52,770 --> 00:09:54,530
cross-district or major crimes.

