Luo Weizhao?

188
00:10:16,530 --> 00:10:17,250
Chief Zhang.

189
00:10:17,370 --> 00:10:19,060
This is Tao Ze speaking. How can I help?

190
00:10:19,730 --> 00:10:20,770
