Help!

199
00:10:49,530 --> 00:10:50,850
Robber!

200
00:10:51,250 --> 00:10:52,340
-Give it to me.
-Help!

201
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,180
-Help!
-Shut up!

202
00:10:53,180 --> 00:10:54,060
Robber!

203
00:10:54,850 --> 00:10:56,010
