229
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:11,820
Who are you?

230
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:13,130
A kind citizen.

231
00:12:13,730 --> 00:12:14,420
Bring him away.

232
00:12:14,490 --> 00:12:15,100
Hello?

233
00:12:15,610 --> 00:12:16,300
-Let's go.
-Captain Luo.

234
00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:18,220
