266
00:13:16,700 --> 00:13:18,610
One hundred thousand? As in money?

267
00:13:18,890 --> 00:13:19,610
Do you have the photo?

268
00:13:19,700 --> 00:13:20,300
Yes.

269
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:27,130
That paper note

270
00:13:27,820 --> 00:13:29,130
